{
  "3059070": {
    "name": "The Headliners",
    "steam_appid": 3059070,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/aa20b59372a1d7dbbe0304f264e1007e.avif?t=1761229580\" width=600 height=106 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/c96801f30c69f1c12d07387fb7561e74.poster.avif?t=1761229580\" width=600 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/c96801f30c69f1c12d07387fb7561e74.webm?t=1761229580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/c96801f30c69f1c12d07387fb7561e74.mp4?t=1761229580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >纽约正遭受神秘生物的袭击，你和你那1到8人的勇敢记者团队必须冒着生命危险，拍摄震撼的照片，并设法逃出生天，才能登上新闻头条！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/ae20903cba2621c04da88509eef77dfe.avif?t=1761229580\" width=600 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/b7c9a2ba91a2fe94180812152e3cd940.poster.avif?t=1761229580\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/b7c9a2ba91a2fe94180812152e3cd940.webm?t=1761229580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/b7c9a2ba91a2fe94180812152e3cd940.mp4?t=1761229580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索废弃而危险的纽约街道，进入建筑物，搜寻每一个阴暗的巷子和隐蔽的角落，寻找值得拍摄的场景。危险无处不在，随时保持警惕。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/edebe2e0ecc5d5c3fb06c575bfeb6d3a.avif?t=1761229580\" width=600 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/9e33b5244f1cafd5cb383b620e3bc3ad.poster.avif?t=1761229580\" width=594 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/9e33b5244f1cafd5cb383b620e3bc3ad.webm?t=1761229580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/9e33b5244f1cafd5cb383b620e3bc3ad.mp4?t=1761229580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你们每个人手里都有一台相机。你可以选择拍摄毁灭的景象、外星入侵者，甚至是你的队友被生物攻击的瞬间。如何捕捉混乱的画面，全由你决定！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/12299f4cc97e39dcc9a8cb10c29597a8.avif?t=1761229580\" width=600 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/6f054d5fea2d531155cecc86ee3df106.poster.avif?t=1761229580\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/6f054d5fea2d531155cecc86ee3df106.webm?t=1761229580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/6f054d5fea2d531155cecc86ee3df106.mp4?t=1761229580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你成功活着逃出来，你可以回顾你的照片，祈祷它们能登上头条。你从3张新闻证开始，每次任务都会用掉一张。只有通过登上头条，你才能获得更多证件，继续这场危险的旅程</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/226765728b5edf27b7975d482cd7baba.avif?t=1761229580\" width=684 height=64 /></span></p>",
